    "description": "欢迎来到克瑞因大陆，《克瑞因的纷争》是一款以卡牌战斗和roguelike玩法为核心，同时加入RPG元素的二次元风格冒险游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/b0b12bf76cd8dd16ab2b0fc16174f99e.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=608 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/b0b12bf76cd8dd16ab2b0fc16174f99e.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/b0b12bf76cd8dd16ab2b0fc16174f99e.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>魔族的侵略正席卷大陆，城外的森林里魔物肆虐。处于战火中的梅比乌斯王国得到了伟大预言的启示，找到能够拯救王国的勇者，从魔族的战火中拯救世界。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/2aafb2c71a3b3246572d0db9bbc4ca64.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=608 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/2aafb2c71a3b3246572d0db9bbc4ca64.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/2aafb2c71a3b3246572d0db9bbc4ca64.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/3a38c666691e2ff5c56f8d8b60c60af0.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/3a38c666691e2ff5c56f8d8b60c60af0.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/3a38c666691e2ff5c56f8d8b60c60af0.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在游戏中，你可以自由地在这片神秘的大陆上探索。就像哥伦布发现新大陆那样，你也会在克瑞因大陆中遇见各种各样新奇的事，但是不是好事就不好说了。<br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/9295008fe1633348aa94f3a1cb698984.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=608 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/9295008fe1633348aa94f3a1cb698984.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/9295008fe1633348aa94f3a1cb698984.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在《克瑞因的纷争》里，你要经常面临各种敌人的攻击，请构筑属于自己的卡组应对各种战斗！总数达到500+的卡牌种类让你随时替换不同体系，面对劲敌游刃有余。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/d616bb57e1163953a7d2d3f0b5e5c424.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/d616bb57e1163953a7d2d3f0b5e5c424.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/d616bb57e1163953a7d2d3f0b5e5c424.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/126a2411415fc71a46218880f6ab45b3.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/126a2411415fc71a46218880f6ab45b3.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/126a2411415fc71a46218880f6ab45b3.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/b1eabc646c605af2c9294a7731975212.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=608 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/b1eabc646c605af2c9294a7731975212.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/b1eabc646c605af2c9294a7731975212.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏中还加入精灵系统，随机地图，技能养成，任意关卡，卡牌附魔融合，背包道具等多种元素。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/ffcb4439f95d4ca1f01709f41dabf3c1.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/ffcb4439f95d4ca1f01709f41dabf3c1.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/ffcb4439f95d4ca1f01709f41dabf3c1.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/7398e0177846e5cc9827d047ee52d058.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/7398e0177846e5cc9827d047ee52d058.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/7398e0177846e5cc9827d047ee52d058.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/d48270b79ecc3d459869bdb150877478.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=608 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/d48270b79ecc3d459869bdb150877478.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/d48270b79ecc3d459869bdb150877478.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏配合Roguelike的玩法机制，死亡后可获得上一局遗留的资源，重新踏上征途。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/356b0f1d154b3dfbd4991d1d8768c526.poster.avif?t=1725002505\" width=608 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/356b0f1d154b3dfbd4991d1d8768c526.webm?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081450/extras/356b0f1d154b3dfbd4991d1d8768c526.mp4?t=1725002505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>肉鸽+卡牌+RPG的奇妙组合，丰富你的游戏体验。<br></li><li>架空式魔幻世界，游戏剧情丰富，把握好自己的选择！<br></li><li>超过500+的卡牌肆意组合，搜集，升级，进化，组成专属于你的最佳卡组！<br></li><li>认养可爱的小精灵，旅途和战斗都助你一臂之力！<br></li><li>开放世界地图让你随意探索，可能偶遇随机Boss！</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入游戏讨论：</h2>官方B站：Another Indie<br>官方微博：@克瑞因的纷争<br>官方公众号：Another Indie<br>官方游戏QQ群（赫尔姆）：145890834<br>官方游戏QQ群（梅比乌斯）：970747208<br>官方游戏QQ群（尼尔海姆）：724822617",
